{"tid":1782164,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"奧斯爾號召穆斯林關心新疆維吾爾族被迫害，中國網民群起杯葛","createTime":"2019-12-13T17:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T01:04:10.000Z","uid":214261,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"91b4970a77a321ba92b34964d9e3577a7714c204","tid":1782164,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T17:24:52.000Z","msg":"體嘢報道：<br />\n <br />\n阿仙奴球星奧斯爾（Mesut Ozil）在個人Twitter聲援被中共迫害的新疆維吾爾人，並質問穆斯林何不團結支持他們、反抗中共對維吾爾人的勞改營政策。中國內地網民和球迷聞訊後，紛紛與奧斯爾割席，有關他的貼吧更被關閉。目前英超賽會、阿仙奴官方沒有回應其言論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屬於土耳其裔的奧斯爾，在Tweet裏以象徵東突厥斯坦的旗幟（被中共視為新疆獨立運動的象徵）為背景，並寫上個人感想。他認為，西方世界居然比穆斯林內部更關心新疆維吾爾人的際遇，他對此感到驚訝。奧斯爾既反對中共強行迫使維吾爾族進入勞改營，並引用伊斯蘭教聖人阿里（Imam Ali）的話，呼籲所有穆斯林齊心向外反映中共的壓迫政策：「如你未能制止不公，亦要播其惡行於眾。」<br />\n <br />\n在近數星期，美國《紐約時報》、BBC《廣角鏡》（Panorama）節目先後獲得了一批外洩的中國官方文件，揭露所謂新疆「再教育營」的運作細節。由於數年前新疆爆發多宗民族衝突和恐怖襲擊，中共在近三年內建立數以百計的再教育營。外界估計，大約有100萬人未經審判就被拘押，其中大多數都是維吾爾族穆斯林。而且，在營內政府對被捕人士施以全天候監控、反覆灌輸洗腦、強制勞動等政策。有關報道引起國際媒體普遍關注。<br />\n<br />\n奧斯爾的言論立即引來中國網民不滿，後者認為他此舉無疑是支持疆獨、分裂中國，並群起發動杯葛行動。但在報道刊出之際，奧斯爾的微博並未關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sportsyeah.hk/2019/12/14/%e5%a5%a7%e6%96%af%e7%88%be%e8%99%9f%e5%8f%ac%e7%a9%86%e6%96%af%e6%9e%97%e9%97%9c%e5%bf%83%e6%96%b0%e7%96%86%e4%ba%ba%e8%a2%ab%e8%bf%ab%e5%ae%b3%ef%bc%8c%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e7%b6%b2%e6%b0%91%e7%be%a4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsportsyeah.hk%2F2019%2F12%2F14%2F%25e5%25a5%25a7%25e6%2596%25af%25e7%2588%25be%25e8%2599%259f%25e5%258f%25ac%25e7%25a9%2586%25e6%2596%25af%25e6%259e%2597%25e9%2597%259c%25e5%25bf%2583%25e6%2596%25b0%25e7%2596%2586%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e8%25bf%25ab%25e5%25ae%25b3%25ef%25bc%258c%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e7%25b6%25b2%25e6%25b0%2591%25e7%25be%25a4%2F&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIEBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=3be96feb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sportsyeah.hk/2019/12/14/%e5%a5%a7%e6%96%af%e7%88%be%e8%99%9f%e5%8f%ac%e7%a9%86%e6%96%af%e6%9e%97%e9%97%9c%e5%bf%83%e6%96%b0%e7%96%86%e4%ba%ba%e8%a2%ab%e8%bf%ab%e5%ae%b3%ef%bc%8c%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e7%b6%b2%e6%b0%91%e7%be%a4/</a><br />\n<br />\n阿記好波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n足球=政治啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1db74c7191004d16ee6daf63f0eebeef4778f5","tid":1782164,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T17:25:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e553b8a0be1d39a47afd2a3d4f90beaf404bdbc3","tid":1782164,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T17:30:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"954cade507f8821ef5690853dde8e5eb26026477","tid":1782164,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T17:38:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ca3c6126d796c5b9b366fe1de6580d321920fa90","tid":1782164,"uid":304726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T17:41:46.000Z","msg":"我燒世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ca758f1cae0e1ece372b6e3e199db7be42607c","tid":1782164,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T17:48:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5cde5bf33e8a12d91f0b0735186be5f9a21ef645","tid":1782164,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T17:50:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c4f8285805331b079adb43b3799e67001f56e5bd","tid":1782164,"uid":101507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T17:52:34.000Z","msg":"波台手足一齊出嚟撐燒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14776a184f717ec92b38e2c358304c03648babfd","tid":1782164,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T17:53:00.000Z","msg":"PUsh"},{"pid":"691be7502c3ed67ac951ab45c11739a995f875c7","tid":1782164,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T1